//BUDGET COMMANDS:
### Create a new budget
POST http://localhost:8080/api/budgets
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Groceries",
  "amount": 300.00
}

### Get all budgets
GET http://localhost:8080/api/budgets

### Get a budget by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/budgets/1

### Update a budget by ID
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/budgets/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Groceries",
  "amount": 350.00
}

### Delete a budget by ID
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/budgets/1

