//GOAL COMMANDS:
### Create a new goal
POST http://localhost:8080/api/goals
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Vacation",
  "targetAmount": 2000.00,
  "currentAmount": 500.00,
  "description": "I need a good vacation."
}

### Get all goals
GET http://localhost:8080/api/goals

### Get a goal by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/goals/1

### Update a goal by ID
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/goals/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Vacation",
  "targetAmount": 2500.00,
  "currentAmount": 600.00,
  "description": "I need a good vacation."
}

### Delete a goal by ID
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/goals/1


